Package com.dufuna.berlin.juwonadeyemi.lekki.model

package com.dufuna.berlin.juwonadeyemi.lekki.model
This package contains the model class for Lekki properties. The LekkiProperty class represents Lekki properties with various attributes. It provides methods to access and modify the property details, and it also includes methods for object comparison and retrieval.

The attributes of the LekkiProperty class include property ID, address, type, number of bedrooms, number of sitting rooms, number of kitchens, number of bathrooms, number of toilets, property owner, description, valid from date, and valid to date.

The class includes methods for setting and getting these attributes, as well as methods for comparing two LekkiProperty objects and generating a hash code based on the property ID. Additionally, the toString method provides a formatted string representation of the LekkiProperty object.
